{
  "texts": [
    "To this end, the streamed response from the Finalize agent is reviewed paragraph-wise by another LLM to ensure consistency with the previous context and to eliminate incorrect content.",
    "This approach effectively overcomes the common limitations of fluent but factually inaccurate formulations [43,44].ChatDRex utilizes gpt-oss-20b [45], a highly capable LLM developed by OpenAI and optimized for helpful responses.",
    "It is hosted through a self-hosted Ollama [46].",
    "We use Ollama behind a self-hosted OpenWebUI 6.",
    "Furthermore, ChatDRex's multi-agent architecture is designed to be flexible, allowing the integration of new and improved LLMs at the individual agent level as they become available."
  ]
}